metadata.name: Image of Plants #P002
metadata.description:
Concept This painting “Imaginary Plants” was inspired by the physical characteristics of plants in an 
ecosystem and the combination of the artist's artistic creation experience that stimulated skills, 
thoughts, knowledge, and imagination to create of imaginary plants. The painting expressed the 
relationship of the natural balance of artist’s attitude and reflects the nature reality.  This painting was a 
two-dimensional traditional Thai painting category that create by charcoal crayon drawing technique on 
synthetic rubber foam board and paper.
